{"tid":594711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港生活成本全球第四高","createTime":"2018-03-16T05:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T07:51:10.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e0129dfe4ea23a1ec28788532660cfcb0d7b30","tid":594711,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/130821_5fb7a9348c98b8206c13fb4e2b440a31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F130821_5fb7a9348c98b8206c13fb4e2b440a31.png&h=7c1fd137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經濟學人智庫公布2018年度《全球生活成本調查》，香港的生活成本為全球第四高，高於挪威奧斯陸等傳統物價較高的城市。新加坡則再度成為全球生活成本最高的城市。<br />\n<br />\n調查涵蓋全球133個城市，以紐約的消費水平作基準，比較超過150項商品及服務價格。其中，香港的生活成本指數達111點，即生活成本較紐約高11%，排名雖較去年跌兩位，但仍排於全球第四位【表】。<br />\n<br />\n獅城居首 滬僅列21<br />\n<br />\n至於首3位生活成本最高的城市分別是新加坡、巴黎，以及蘇黎世，另外首爾及悉尼則排第六位及第十位。《調查》的編輯羅克珊娜（Roxana Slavcheva）稱，「新加坡反映出亞洲區的發展趨勢，即亞洲樞紐城市大多也是全球生活成本最高的城市。」<br />\n<br />\n港人熟悉的東京及大阪同列第11位，中國生活成本最高的城市為上海，排全球21位。至於美國則未有城市打入十大，紐約及洛杉磯分列第13及14位，主要因為美元走弱。<br />\n<br />\n報告又提及，香港、首爾及東京為全球購買必需品成本最高的3大城市。雖然新加坡的整體生活成本最高，特別是買車及購買衣服方面，但當地有部分產品及服務，如個人護理及家庭用品等，其實較區內其他城市為低。<br />\n<br />\n全球生活水平最低的城市則為敍利亞的大馬士革及委內瑞拉的卡拉卡斯，其中大馬士革的生活成本只是紐約的26%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E9%AB%98-212000016.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%25AB%2598-212000016.html&d=700AN3tn0fjhpXEbPZT%2BlcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=83ad33dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E9%AB%98-212000016.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eiu.com/topic/worldwide-cost-of-living\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eiu.com%2Ftopic%2Fworldwide-cost-of-living&d=700AN3tn0fjhpXEbPZT%2BlcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=00b4aff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eiu.com/topic/worldwide-cost-of-living</a>"},{"pid":"d36590e313ed4bc644a70694cba908c60eb2e536","tid":594711,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"香港先第四？"},{"pid":"3c96925294bc447eecd22c1e84c3c1e848a03066","tid":594711,"uid":150021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"057850991e5f11b28132235607be989bbc0fe3a2","tid":594711,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"計埋租金樓價未"},{"pid":"f108960414ce7868988ab1659ed5b8cd9a71dfb7","tid":594711,"uid":17765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"話香港稅低 買嘢平嘅香港閪死撚咗去邊？"},{"pid":"b7c1c217f492742f25a7e4302410731ef0e009f4","tid":594711,"uid":125258,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"雖然新加坡的整體生活成本最高，特別是買車及購買衣服方面<br />\n<br />\n買車都計埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁一定高架人地政府收咁重稅 <br />\n其實新加坡食野普遍平過香港<br />\nMetropolis 附近foodcourt $30蚊HKD就食到lunch<br />\n仲要人地有PR可以住組屋，又慳返一大筆"},{"pid":"66ce06e4229c70f51deb82dec05518900a335212","tid":594711,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99cc767fbda60cf1e5d1eec72524de8e3fe1ebc8","tid":594711,"uid":125258,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f108960414ce7868988ab1659ed5b8cd9a71dfb7","tid":594711,"uid":17765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"話香港稅低 買嘢平嘅香港閪死撚咗去邊？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"冇衝突架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買野的確係平<br />\n只係